# EduMIPS64 help topics index.
#
# This file is the single hand-maintained metadata for the in-shell help
# browser (`help topics`, `help <topic>`). The topic content itself is
# the actual reStructuredText source of the user manual, copied into
# the JAR by the Gradle `processResources` task; the build is hermetic
# and the docs never drift from the chapters they ship.
#
# Format: <topic-id><TAB><rst-filename><TAB><human title>
# Lines starting with '#' or empty lines are ignored.
overview	index.rst	EduMIPS64 user manual - landing page
cli	cli-interface.rst	The interactive command-line shell
syntax	source-files-format.rst	Source-file format and assembler syntax
instructions	instructions.rst	The supported MIPS64 instruction set
fpu	fpu.rst	Floating-point unit support
examples	examples.rst	Code examples
swing	user-interface-swing.rst	The Swing desktop user interface
web	user-interface-web.rst	The web user interface

